### Create an Agent
POST http://localhost:8000/agents/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Storyteller",
    "system_prompt": "You are a creative storyteller. Tell short, engaging stories based on user prompts.",
    "voice_id": "shimmer"
}

### List Agents
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/

### Get Agent
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/1

### Update Agent
PATCH http://localhost:8000/agents/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Creative Bard"
}

### Chat with Agent (Text)
POST http://localhost:8000/agents/1/chat
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data
# Form Parameter: message="Tell me a story about a brave knight."

### Voice Chat (Mocking an upload would require a file)
# POST http://localhost:8000/agents/1/voice-chat
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data
# Form Parameter: audio=@path/to/audio.wav
